
<!--Header-->
<div class ="container-fluid content">      
  <div class="row bordered">
      <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class ="content-header">    
              <h3> Are you getting the most out of your website ? </h3>
              
              <h4>A list of reasearch backed key aspects which could make or break your website.<br><br>
              One of our experts will personally check key aspects of your website and let you know what can be done <b>right now</b>
              to make sure that your website is optimized to turn visitors into paying customers.
              </h4>
              <h3 class ="subtitle "> Here’s why you could be shooting your business<br> in the foot </h3>
          </div>   
      </div>    
  </div>
</div>
<!--Attention --> 
<div class ="container-fluid first bordered">  
  <div class="row">
      <div class = "col-md-6 icon">
        <div class="left">
          <%= image_tag('eye-p.png', class:'img-responsive') %>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag('2.jpg', class:'img-responsive show-me') %>
      </div> 
      <div class= "col-md-6 text">      
        <div class="container-fluid">
          
          <div class="animation-element slide-left testimonial">
            <div class="header">
              <div class="right">
                <h3> Your website might not be communicating the right thing straight away. </h3>
                <h4>The human attention span is around 7 seconds. Most of your website visitors are likely to leave your website in the first 7 seconds if you can’t pass this test.
               <br> <br> What you communicate and how you do it in those first few secconds
            is vital to converting visitors into paying customers.
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!--Mobile --> 
<div class ="container first bordered">      
  <div class="row">
       
    <div class="left">
        <%= image_tag('phone-p.png', class:'img-responsive') %>
      </div>
      
      <div class= "col-md-6 text">      
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="animation-element slide-left testimonial">
            <div class="header">
              <div class="right">
                <h3>If your website is not easy to read on mobile</h3>
                <h4>As much as 59% of smartphone users will likely <i>never</i> return to your website.<br><br> By 2018 almost 80% of internet usage will be mobile. You could possibly be missing out on literally thousands of potential clients.
                <br><br>In this report you'll see if your website is easy to read on mobile and what you can do about it if it's not. 
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class = "col-md-6 icon">
      <%= image_tag('mobile.jpg', class:'img-responsive show-me') %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>   
<!--Speed --> 
<div class ="container first">      
  <div class="row">
      <div class = "col-md-6 icon ">
        <div class="left">
          <%= image_tag('watch-p.png', class:'img-responsive') %>
        </div>
          <%= image_tag('1.jpg', class:'img-responsive show-me') %>
      </div> 
      <div class= "col-md-6 text ">      
        <div class="container-fluid">
          
          <div class="animation-element slide-left testimonial ">
            <div class="header">
              <div class="right">
                <h3> Your website might not load fast enough </h3>
                <h4>If your website is taking longer than 3 secconds to load, as much as 40% of your visitors will leave your 
                  page no matter how great your product or service is.
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



<!--CTA 2 -->
<div class = "container">
  <div class ="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
    <div class="cta2">
      <btn class="btn btn-primary btn-lg submission2" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">ANALYZE MY WEBSITE</btn>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">

    <!-- Modal content-->
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title">Free Website Checkup</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <%= render "contacts/form2"%>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

